  "notes": "Pipeline order: Enrich (5 runs × 3 items = 15 items) → Batch (3 runs × 5 items = 15 items) → Cluster. Enrich nodes use Header Auth credential (literal URL, no $env). Batch/Cluster nodes use $env.CE_SITE_URL + $env.MESODMA_API_KEY. For 60 items/day on Vercel Hobby: run this workflow 4× daily (02:00, 08:00, 14:00, 20:00 UTC). Synthesis NOT wired — manual approval required."
